Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll head to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about? I'm at the onsen right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-sama, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The prize from the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do anything because I have this ticket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please read this book aloud for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou-kin and Barusu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eloping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou-kin, it's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this erotic novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at that place, take your glasses off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Barusu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou-kin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you d-don't ne-need to take them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I - can - fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\fnGentium Book Basic\fs90\be5\pos(650,305)\c&HFDFEFA&\3c&H46A851&}It's my First Time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be in such a situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in the male's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know exactly why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow managed to fool them by saying Punyuru had returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, come here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}were{\i0} here, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when I thought there wouldn't be any people here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how do you know my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just friends and close classmates.{this line needs work}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you didn't have a relationship with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, she has been having fun attending school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be quite worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you find a parent that doesn't care about their child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I am talking about that cute Subaru of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing your face really pisses me off after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I will stay in the same bath with you any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait here until he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:05:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it's a training camp for eloping or curing my gynophobia or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your father came as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like there was some sort of reason for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Say Konoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something that perfectly resembles a girl's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose is this anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually I'm that type of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of excuse is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru's underwear were like this as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You had this type of relationship with Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Punyuru-chan will come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure of it. Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I am having temporary memory loss for some parts of last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was I sleeping in the bath, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is Punyuru-chan really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are only leaning your neck that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why is your neck bending like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I had a stiff neck while I slept...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We were a bit late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was choosing glasses, so it took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Punyuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see{changing meet>see} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Subaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him run some errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai- Hey, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Suzutsuki Kanade, why are you holding hands with idiot-chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he is my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you were lying right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He is actually a gynophobic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, you seem to know as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say Jirou-kun, won't you play the shooting game in that shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, I shot and killed the rabbit.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean shot and dropped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I'm Usami, not a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there are more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be an event soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this event?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A yukata beauty contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battle royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a fireworks display at the end{after that at the closure}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something to look forward to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Punyuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't see her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She was with her just awhile ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...?{What is this...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Konoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now do a tongue twister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Butler's art of erasing memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Butler's art of erasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Barusu, I want to see everything of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Konoe doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the anniversary of her mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The young master of Takanashi's house is near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran off to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of things happened when we married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she is sleeping in the graveyard of the Takanashis'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kanade-ojousama goes out on a trip, then Subaru must follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So if she does that, Subaru wouldn't be able to visit the grave on the anniversary of her mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Suzutsuki was doing this for Konoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to participate in the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go and enlist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to keep it a secret, from you at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had to get rid of Nagare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,About your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Takanashi Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was always worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wondering whether I would make proper friends or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as my mother had worried about, I never had any friends. {As you can see, i never had any friends, like my mother was worried about.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always unsociable and distant from people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always hiding the fact that you were a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried not to be in contact with anyone in order to prevent them from discovering your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Jirou, please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to come here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this, you'll fall unconscious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to be worried anymore. {she is talking about her mother&#60&#60ara}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I decided I wouldn't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to introduce you to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As my first friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not here anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be reminded of it if I came here with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I would cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want to come here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Konoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you introduce me to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,About me, to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakamachi Kinjirou, he is Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He is... my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Jirou, you are my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised{Heard} you hit your head after falling down when you went to pick up Punyuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To the battle royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're competing as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the grand prize will be a large stuffed sheep plush doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe loves that as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And a kiss from the Yukata beauty contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to reintroduce the Yukata beauty contest winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Punyuru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, for the silent sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't accept someone like you receiving a kiss from Punyuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept that type of development with anyone but you and Subaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, everyone that's a battle royal participant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Line up at the starting line...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill, kill, kill, kill... Kiss, kiss, kiss... Kill, kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The rule is very simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're hit with a single bit of paint, your game is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner receives the grand prize and kiss from the Miss Yukata beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First the solo players...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First we have to deal with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, senpai, you were over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl gets drunk from drinking carbonated drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Usami-senpai is a very maiden-like person{very young girl typish}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge and take, drunken fist stripping{unclothing}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Drunken fist stripping{unclothing}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She has this drunken behavior of being able to strip{unclothe} someone while she is drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Usame-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw an opening{I have my chance}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's battle of strength, then I am on top of you. {arashi: LOL in more than one way XD }
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These eyes that wear glasses can overcome anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you could win against my tickling attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry cause I'll leave your glasses alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the glasses, just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we were the only ones left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you surrender, I'll consider letting this hostage go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is just cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What sins have they committed?{What sins do you say that little fellow has?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the, this is a... déjà vu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared them because I thought something like that might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, how good are your preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Jirou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried your best even though you were a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were cool for a moment there{little bit}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you win...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who won the battle royal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzutsuki Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get up {even though I tried to make you}so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any weird intentions by it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't secretly watching your sleeping face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Suzutsuki and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakuru-chan went on a rampage, undressing people around her since she thought your glasses were broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama went to tell her that they weren't, so everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it will go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama gave this to me as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's creepy after all.{It is clumsy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy{Clumsy}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get its loveliness{the lovingness in this}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a proper look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is so lovable about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel like the summer is about to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in the middle of August.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the summer will end in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel lonely that the summer vacation will end but,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can live with you or Ojou-sama when the second term comes around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it seems that the second term will be be a hectic one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am already used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That has become our everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? We'll always be friends! {FRIENDZONED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be just friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like being embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou-kun, please watch over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of shyness play is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Mayo Chiki:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 9: I will go out on a journey for awhile.
